objects.description: [NotPetya](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0368)'s initial infection vector for the June 27, 2017 compromise was a backdoor in the Ukrainian tax accounting software M.E.Doc.(Citation: Talos Nyetya June 2017)(Citation: US-CERT NotPetya 2017)(Citation: Talos Nyetya MEDoc 2017)
